data.description: If you're looking for the perfect 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a pool, this is it! These owners have taken care of everything. You will enjoy the open floor plan with tiled floors throughout. The spacious primary bedroom has an updated primary bathroom attached. There are two additional spacious bedrooms with large closet space and a full, updated bath. The kitchen is updated and offers stainless appliances. Pool and deck were refinished in 2022 and offers a lanai. Pool pump & filtration system were updated in 2023. Newer solar, AC, windows and so much more. You are going to love this home sweet home!
